snippet.title: Space Outpost
snippet.description: The Space Outpost is home to a futuristic power station nestled inside of an asteroid crater. This area houses large shops, and is the future home to the Rocket Monsters Intergalactic Space Port. Owning or renting property in the Space Outpost sector allows for discounts in the NFT marketplace.
